quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  70,40,"Mi woondirii JeyЙ—o fuЙ—irЙ—e e mutirЙ—e On, pellet, ko Men hattanЙ“e"
  70,41,"wattitirgol Й“e ko Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude, Men siforaa ronkugol [Й—um]"
  70,42,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e fija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e kammbirananoo"
  70,43,"Гұalnde Й“e yaltiroyta e genaale Й—en heГұaare, wa si tawii ko kaaЖҙe (sanamu) Й“e woni wugganaade"
  70,44,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e no heli, koyeera no suddi Й“e. Ko nden Гұalaande woni ko Й“e kammbirananoo"
  71,1,"Men nulii Nuuhu haa e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, wonnde : \"Jertin yimЙ“e maa Й“en, ado lette muusuЙ—e arde e maЙ“Й“e"
  71,2,"O maakani [Й“e] : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi jertinoowo on Й“annguЙ—o"
  71,3,"wonnde yo on rewu Allah, hulon Mo, Й—oftoЙ—on lam"
  71,4,"O haforanay on junuubi mon Й—in, O nenna on haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. [Ko woni tun] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si tawii hiЙ—on anndunoo"
  71,5,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi noddirii yimЙ“e am Й“en jemma e Гұalorma"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am ndun Й“eydaali Й“e, si wanaa dogugol"
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi Й“e fii no Hafaranaa Й“e, Й“e waЙ—ay kolli maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka nder noppi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e buumora comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e deppitoo, Й“e townitora townitaadee"
  71,8,Refti mi noddirii Й“e e kene
  71,9,"Refti mi feГұГұinani Й“e, mi gunndii Й“e gunndaadee"
  71,10,"Mi wi'i [Й“e] : \"Insinanee Joomi mon, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoow"
